{
  "stem": "12666.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when the others workers help her, they say ah, that Russian swine can die.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's all right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because the slave laborer who were not Jewish, they had a little square and it was written there O-S-T.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That means Eastern slave.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And my uncle was among those slaves too, where the American government and the British government was turning these slaves back to Stalin to be executed.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my uncle heard those rumors and he fled from the refugee camp and hid in the forest.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Next day, American MPs came in and dragged the Russians into buses to take them to the Communist Soviet Union lines.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And some of them broke the window and cut their wrists to commit suicide.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Our medics fixed them up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Well, after my uncle saw that, he fled to Munich and found a German family that took him in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he somehow managed to make an announcement in the newspaper in New York.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My mother read that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And she right away called me at Nuremberg and say, listen, if you have time, your uncle that you have never seen with his wife and child, they are at this address, living in a private German home.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I took a weekend off and I went to see my uncle for the first time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was telling me what happened to him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was in the same regiment of my father, fighting the Civil War, and he was sent for reconnaissance.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was cut off, because you know, when civil war happens, the lines are not well established.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father couldn't find him, had to retreat under the pressure.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my uncle and his men hid in some mines near Odessa there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were hiding during the day.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
